  "subject": "Change Vagrant default provider",
  "commit_message": "Change Vagrant default provider\n\nVagrant uses VirtualBox as default provider, but given that it's not\nfully supported in this project its better to change that behaviour.\nThis change makes Libvirt as default Vagrant provider.\n\nChange-Id: Ib80636f8c595280d425901a8914548d199606fdc\nSigned-off-by: Victor Morales <victor.morales@intel.com>\nIssue-ID: MULTICLOUD-301\n",
